

Purpose: Git repository hosting version Control

Access Information:
- URL: http://git.lab.local
- Location (VM): apps.lab.local
- Container/Service Name: gitea (Docker container)

Credentials:
- Admin Username: admin
- Admin Password Location: [Stored in password manager]

Technical Details:
- Database: PostgreSQL (gitea database)
- Configuration Files: /opt/docker/gitea/
- Data Location: /opt/docker/gitea/
- Log Location: /opt/dpcker/gitea/gitea/log

Common Operations:

Restart: docker compose restart gitea

View Logs: docker logs gitea -f

Check Status: docker ps | grep gitea

Backup: tar -czf gitea-backup.tar.gz /opt/docker/gitea

Dependencies: 
- Requires: Postgresql
- Required by: n/a

Notes: - Version control 
